# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok bangladeshi state minister for energy and mineral resources <unk> mosharraf hossain sunday invited international oil companies to explore the potential oil and gas fields in the offshore areas of bangladesh in the bay of bengal .
# ::alignments
(ii / invite-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Mosharraf"
                  :op2 "Hossain")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (s / state
                        :location (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Bangladesh")))
                  :ARG2 (m / minister
                        :topic (a / and
                              :op1 (e / energy)
                              :op2 (r / resource
                                    :mod (m2 / mineral))))))
      :ARG1 (c2 / company
            :mod (ii2 / international)
            :mod (o / oil))
      :ARG2 (e2 / explore-01
            :ARG0 c2
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (f / field
                        :mod (o2 / oil))
                  :op2 (f2 / field
                        :mod (g / gas))
                  :mod (p2 / potential)
                  :location (a3 / area
                        :mod (o3 / offshore)
                        :location c
                        :location (b / bay
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Bengal")))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok seismologists warned sunday that a major aftershock could hit populated areas in southwestern china as rescue workers struggled sunday to reach victims of a powerful earthquake which killed at least ### people .
# ::alignments
(w / warn-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :mod (s / seismology))
      :ARG1 (p2 / possible-01
            :ARG1 (h / hit-01
                  :ARG0 (a / aftershock
                        :ARG1-of (m / major-02))
                  :ARG1 (a2 / area
                        :ARG1-of (p3 / populate-01)
                        :location (s2 / southwest
                              :part-of (c / country
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "China"))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s3 / sunday))
      :time (s4 / struggle-02
            :ARG0 (p4 / person
                  :ARG0-of (w2 / work-01
                        :ARG1 (r / rescue-01)))
            :ARG1 (r2 / reach-01
                  :ARG0 p4
                  :ARG1 (v / victim
                        :poss (e / earthquake
                              :ARG1-of (p5 / powerful-02)
                              :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
                                    :ARG1 (p6 / person
                                          :quant (a3 / at-least
                                                :op1 2))))))))

                        :name (n / name

                  :ARG0 c2

                        :mod (w / world)
                        :mod (c3 / commerce)))

                  :ARG1 (q / qualify-02
                        :ARG1 c2
                        :ARG2 (b / become-01
                              :ARG1 c2

                                    :ord (o3 / ordinal-entity
                                          :value -1)
                                    :ARG2-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                          :ARG0 c2
                                          :ARG1 o2)))))))

                  :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 c
                                    :ARG2 (a / ambassador
                                          :location (c2 / city
                                                :name (n2 / name
                                                      :op1 "Washington")))))
                        :ARG2 (w / wife)))

                        :quant 10000
                        :unit (d / dollar)))

                  :poss (m3 / man
                        :mod c
                        :location (c3 / city

                                    :op1 "San"
                                    :op2 "Diego"))

                                    :quant 2
                                    :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                                          :ARG2 (p5 / person
                                                :ARG0-of (h3 / hijack-01)))))
                        :ARG0-of (a2 / assist-01
                              :ARG1 p5)))
            :ARG1-of (b2 / believe-01
                  :ARG0 p2)
            :mod (c4 / charitable))

            :weekday (s2 / saturday)))

                                          :ARG1-of h))))))

                                          :value 2)
                                    :poss s))))))
